	<p>Learn how to maximize the lifespan and battery life of your Apple notebook.</p>

	<a href="ipods.html"><img src="http://images.apple.com/batteries/images/ipodfamily.jpg" alt="" width="192" height="126" style="margin: 5px 24px 0;" /></a>
