	<p>Learn how to maximize the lifespan and battery life of your iPod touch, iPod nano, iPod classic, or iPod shuffle.</p>

	<a href="iphone.html"><img src="http://images.apple.com/batteries/images/batteriesiphone.jpg" alt="" width="191" height="114" style="margin: 20px 0 0 45px;" /></a>
